{"tid":2257342,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"鄭中基新歌 <My Only One> 好好Loop","createTime":"2020-10-25T05:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T02:56:51.000Z","uid":245286,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"87bb95c1acdcf79d3199765dfe5a5ddb3a39f5f3","tid":2257342,"uid":245286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:32:42.000Z","msg":"雖然喺隔籬影視台嘅《暖男爸爸》post都有Post過呢隻歌<br />\n但係越聽越覺得，呢隻歌獨立噉聽，都係一隻好值得推介嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n呢隻歌係改編自哥倫比亞男歌手Sebasti&aacute;n Yatra同美國女歌手Isabela Merced (Isabela Moner) 合唱嘅My Only One (或者係最初Sebasti&aacute;n Yatra自己獨唱嘅版本No Hay Nadie M&aacute;s，係西班牙語歌曲嚟嘅)<br />\n<br />\n再唔係失戀慘情歌，都幾治癒嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n旋律幾簡單易記，幾易上口嘅我覺得<br />\n暫時可以公開分享到嘅得半首，各位有興趣可以去各個音樂平台搵完整版本嚟聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (KKBOX、moov、Spotify、itunes嗰啲都已經上曬架)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cljZ3aoGn4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcljZ3aoGn4Y&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=353e82a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cljZ3aoGn4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞：<br />\n今晚星光閃出真愛 夢有光圈記載<br />\n時光機主角發呆 捕捉當下是競賽<br />\n熱戀的心不可掩蓋 齋啡都斟滿愛<br />\n人生充滿意外 每刻感動在腦海<br />\n<br />\n唯獨是你<br />\n一心想把你愛護到極限<br />\n苦中多粒糖 朝晚 抱緊著你<br />\n我很習慣 給你闖進生命裡 沒有圍欄<br />\n<br />\n緣來是友情 尋找愛情<br />\n天 與 地 共享恬靜<br />\n被愛的瞬間 對跖點之間<br />\n有你 牽掛 是我一世 最美的浪漫<br />\nMy only one<br />\nMy only one<br />\n<br />\n街邊的窩心小店<br />\n你給我家的 幸福意識<br />\n有溫暖的記憶 令單調都變色<br />\n我跟你一世 數月曆<br />\n失足的天使<br />\n給我安慰的 我心裡想要的 我真正需要的<br />\n你都知道<br />\n<br />\n唯獨是你<br />\n一心想把你愛護到極限<br />\n苦中多粒糖 朝晚 抱緊著你<br />\n我很習慣 給你闖進生命裡 沒有圍欄<br />\n<br />\n緣來是友情 尋找愛情<br />\n天 與 地 共享恬靜<br />\n被愛的瞬間 對跖點之間<br />\n有你 牽掛 是我一世 最美的浪漫<br />\n<br />\n緣來是愛情 母須證明<br />\n童話 結局 命中註定<br />\n驟雨的瞬間 亂世喘息間<br />\n有你 倚靠 是我一世 最終的浪漫<br />\n<br />\nMy only one, there's no one else<br />\nMy only one, there's no one else<br />\nYou are my only one<br />\nIt's just there's no one else, ouh, uoh My only one<br />\nMy Only<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外再擺埋原曲兩個版本上嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y82H_pgqKdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY82H_pgqKdY&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3f2a5970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y82H_pgqKdY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sD9_l3oDOag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsD9_l3oDOag&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=6eea26d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sD9_l3oDOag</a>"},{"pid":"7e73bbc4afa4e4ba83b9aef16d883ae5881525c3","tid":2257342,"uid":10903,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"幾好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 暴龍哥一定要繼續唱歌呀"},{"pid":"9c056d01c0233be6a6da66b02d7ba32e1e1fcc8e","tid":2257342,"uid":58863,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"好聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張可頤原來已經51歲 仲好索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8294f1dc847c90d929a2b2f22266013874839e8","tid":2257342,"uid":370010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"780233b96ad4a4df81be08e2c2cc7bb2c216fe5c","tid":2257342,"uid":110018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"好想鄭中基再開演唱會"},{"pid":"60eb3a6e6ce5c3e4bcb2206857ae2a71436b5de6","tid":2257342,"uid":245286,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"780233b96ad4a4df81be08e2c2cc7bb2c216fe5c","tid":2